file.name: issue-300.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https://petstore.swagger.io/v2'
  - url: 'http://petstore.swagger.io/v2'
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
paths:
  '/pet/{petId}':
    get:
      summary: Find pet by ID
      operationId: getPetById
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          description: ID of pet to return
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int64
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
        '400':
          description: Invalid ID supplied
        '404':
          description: Pet not found
components:
  schemas:
    Pet:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          example: doggie
        shots:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            example: rabies
            xml:
              name: shot
          xml:
            name: shots
            wrapped: true            
      xml:
        name: Pet
